Other then that I would stick to those badboy two handers. <p>[img]http://www.geocities.com/Hollywood/Studio/7677/mrt1.jpg[/img] </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ustoneribskosterkin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stoneribs Kosterkin</A></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/21/00 4:21:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Preference.</span><hr size=1> I have a twinked 37 warrior atm &amp; my arsenal consists of:<br>
1)Wurmslayer<br>
2)YK<br>
3)Mith 2H<br>
4)Fleshripper (58 ae spell)<br>
str is 177 unbuffed<br>
<br>
I personally like the WS + YK combo but i hear at higher lvls alot of stuff is resistant to YK's so I think I'm gonna get me some stat building 1H. I hit in the 60's &amp; 70's alot with the WS (highest crit being 168 &amp; no crippling blows yet) &amp; I have a fbss also. I switch between sta &amp; dex shoulders &amp; exe hood or skull shaped barbute for the head.(thank god for EE bags hehe)<br>
<br>
you can smack hard with 2h's but i prefer the dual wield hitting with one like a 2h. the WS is very nice <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . No taunting problems here.<br>
